OL,3,CJury sworn in for trial of two
OL,4,Cchildren accused of killing elderly
OL,5,Cdog walker
OL,7,FA jury has been selected and sworn in
OL,8,Fahead of the trial of two children
OL,9,Faccused of killing an 80-year-old man
OL,10,Fwho was injured while walking his dog.
OL,12,FBhim Kohli died in hospital on
OL,13,FSeptember 2 last year, a day after he
OL,14,Fwas allegedly attacked in Franklin
OL,15,FPark near his home in Braunstone Town,
OL,16,Fnear Leicester.
