OL,3,CJury sworn in for trial of two
OL,4,Cchildren accused of killing elderly
OL,5,Cdog walker
OL,7,FA 15-year-old boy is charged with Mr
OL,8,FKohli's murder and manslaughter, while
OL,9,Fa 13-year-old girl is charged with his
OL,10,Fmanslaughter. Neither child can be
OL,11,Fnamed because of their ages.
OL,13,FThe jurors were selected at Leicester
OL,14,FCrown Court on Monday ahead of the
OL,15,Ftrial, which is expected to last
OL,16,Faround six to eight weeks and will be
OL,17,Fheard by High Court judge Mr Justice
OL,18,FTurner.
