OL,3,CJury sworn in for trial of two
OL,4,Cchildren accused of killing elderly
OL,5,Cdog walker
OL,7,FThe jury was told that because of the
OL,8,Fdefendants' ages, the judge and
OL,9,Fbarristers would not be wearing gowns
OL,10,Fand wigs during the trial.
OL,12,FThe youths would also sit at the back
OL,13,Fof the courtroom instead of in the
OL,14,Fdock, jurors heard.
OL,16,FMr Kohli died at Queen's Medical
OL,17,FCentre in Nottingham after the alleged
OL,18,Fattack, which took place while he was
OL,19,Fwalking his dog Rocky.
