OL,7,FHis family said in a statement at the
OL,8,Ftime: "Bhim was a loving husband, dad
OL,9,Fand granddad. He was also a son,
OL,10,Fbrother and uncle.
OL,12,F"He adored his grandkids with all his
OL,13,Fheart and loved spending time with
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,F"He really was such a loving, caring
OL,17,Fperson whose life was centred around
OL,18,Fhis family."
